item.description: About us About us We are Game of Code, we are coders. We are a small team constisting of 3 people who are getting educated in code. We have been workning with JAVA, C#, Html, Css, MySQL , Heroku, Netlify and Javascript. Right now our team is exploring the possibilities of GoHugo and that is the reason for this site. We are a positive team constantly searching for more knowledge in the coding area to become better at what we do.
